\newlabel{fig:operators}{{4}{4}{\textbf {Stabilization operator comparison.} PR and $\alpha $ for reservoir computers with different stabilization operators. All operators drive the system toward collapse (increasing $\alpha $, decreasing PR), following a similar spectral trajectory}{figure.4}{}}
